Visit a Link from a Dashboard Widget

Dashboard builders can link dashboard widgets to Salesforce records or other websites. Visit a link to act on dashboard insights!

Available in: Lightning Experience, Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To visit a dashboard widget link:
Run Reports
Open a dashboard.
Expand a widget. Hover over a widget and click .
Visit the link. From the expanded widget, click >.

The linked widgetâ€™s destination opens.
